name: Log Write Report DB
MSSQL Kernel
query:
SELECT 4                                                         AS DeliveryType,
       send.req_channel                                          AS Channel,
       ''                                                        AS PGCode,
       ''                                                        AS PGDesc,
       Substring(Upper(send.req_batch_id), 1, 20)                AS BatchNo,
       Substring(Upper(send.uid), 1, 20)                         AS RecordID,
       send_record.send_time                                     AS PSendTime,
       send_record.actual_send_time                              AS RSendTime,
       ''                                                        AS CheckFlag,
       ''                                                        AS ErrorMsg,
       1                                                         AS SendFlag,
       send_record.resp_code                                     AS SendStatus,
       0                                                         AS IsRead,
       Substring(send_record.customer_id, 1, 11)                 AS CustID,
       send_record.customer_phone                                AS CustPhoneNum,
       Iif(send.req_channel LIKE '%card%', 'CARDSMS', 'BANKSMS') AS OutSysID,
       CASE
         WHEN send.priority >= 9 THEN 'T'
         WHEN send.priority <= 8
              AND send.priority >= 6 THEN 'G'
         WHEN send.priority < 5 THEN 'C'
       end                                                       AS MsgContentType,
       send.priority                                             AS Priority,
       send_record.content                                       AS MsgContent
FROM   [dbo].[send],
       [dbo].[send_record]
WHERE  send_record.send_uid = send.uid and CAST(send_record.create_time AS date) = DATEADD(day, -1, CAST(GETDATE() AS date))

name: MSSQL Report
query: INSERT INTO [dbo].[DeliveryResultLog](DeliveryPoolUID, DeliverySendUID, DeliverySendRecordUID, Status, Message, SourceType) VALUES(@DeliveryPoolUID, @DeliverySendUID, @DeliverySendRecordUID, @ResponseStatus, @ResponseMessage, 'Realtime')

name: Log HTTP Response
func:
msg.ResponseMessage = msg.payload
msg.ResponseStatus = 0
msg.SendUID = JSON.parse(msg.payload)["sendUid"]

msg.SendRecordUID = JSON.parse(msg.payload)["results"][0]["sendRecordUid"] || null

msg.result = "[GRAVITY][ATOMIC] HTTP Post via Message API success"

msg.payload = {
    "channel": "GRAVITY_SMS_MESSAGE_API",
    "level": "INFO",
    "code": 0,
    "msg": msg.result,
    "time": (new Date()).toJSON(),
    "payload": {
        "DeliveryPoolUID": msg.DeliveryPoolUID,
        "SendUID": msg.SendUID,
        "SendRecordUID": msg.SendRecordUID
    }
}

return msg

name: MSSQL Kernel
query:
SELECT log_operation.user_id                       AS userid,
       'NBP'                                       AS appid,
       1                                           AS logaction,
       'S'                                         AS logresult,
       Cast(log_operation.create_time AS DATETIME) AS logdatetime,
       '0.0.0.0'                                   AS hostip,
       log_operation.client_ip                     AS clientip,
       ''                                          AS remark
FROM   [dbo].[log_operation]
WHERE  log_operation.category = 'signin' and CAST(send_record.create_time AS date) = DATEADD(day, -1, CAST(GETDATE() AS date))

name: MSSQL Kernel
query:
SELECT CONVERT(VARCHAR(8), log_operation.create_time, 112) AS AppDate,
       'NBP'                                       AS AppID,
       (SELECT company.code
        FROM   company
        WHERE  log_operation.before_data IS NOT NULL
               AND Json_value(log_operation.before_data, '$.companyUid') =
                   company.uid)
                                                   AS CompID,
       (SELECT company.NAME
        FROM   company
        WHERE  log_operation.before_data IS NOT NULL
               AND Json_value(log_operation.before_data, '$.companyUid') =
                   company.uid)
                                                   AS CompName,
       department.code                             AS DeptID,
       department.NAME                             AS DeptName,
       Json_value(before_data, '$.userId')         AS EmpID,
       Json_value(before_data, '$.name')           AS EmpName,
       log_operation.function_name                 AS FunID,
       ''                                          AS FunName,
       '人工授權'                              AS GrantType,
       log_operation.text                          AS GrantDesc,
       1                                           AS WorkStatus,
       '在職'                                    AS WorkStatusDesc,
       log_operation.user_id                       AS GrantUserID,
       log_operation.user_name                     GrantUserName,
       ''                                          AS Remark
FROM   log_operation,
       department
WHERE  category = 'permission' 
       AND action_name != 'deleted'
       AND CAST(send_record.create_time AS date) = DATEADD(day, -1, CAST(GETDATE() AS date))

name: MSSQL Kernel
query:
SELECT CONVERT(VARCHAR(8), log_operation.create_time, 112) AS AppDate,
       'NBP'                                               AS AppID,
       CONVERT(VARCHAR(8), log_operation.create_time, 112) AS ReadHRLogDate,
       CONVERT(VARCHAR(8), log_operation.create_time, 108) AS ReadHRLogTime,
       CONVERT(VARCHAR(8), log_operation.create_time, 112) AS DeleteACDate,
       CONVERT(VARCHAR(8), log_operation.create_time, 108) AS DeleteACTime,
       1                                                   AS DeleteACType
FROM   log_operation 
WHERE  CAST(send_record.create_time AS date) = DATEADD(day, -1, CAST(GETDATE() AS date))
AND    category='permission' and action_name='deleted'
